# The Great Big Book of Markua Image Formatting

This book shows how images can be formatted in Markua, and what they look like.

# Just the Plain Image

For this demo book, we will be using the plain image shown below.

Text above the image

![](palm-trees.jpg)

Text below the image

# Just the Plain Image with Alt Text

For this demo book, we will be using the plain image shown below, this time with 
the alt-text of "foo"

Text above the image

{alt: "foo"}
![](palm-trees.jpg)

Text below the image

